Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.25,0:01:38.05,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,When I was a kid, in a crazy dream
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.36,0:01:40.13,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I was gazin' up to the Promised Land
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.13,0:01:44.76,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,僕らのユメの形　ザワメキ出す Heart！ Beat！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.76,0:01:46.77,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Come on let's go to that place
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.11,0:01:48.73,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I just can't stop anymore
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.98,0:01:53.53,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飛びだせ　仄暗い空　fly into the light
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.82,0:01:57.40,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信じたいこの世界に生まれたことが幸せってこと
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.40,0:02:00.00,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新時代へ続く扉を開けるんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.00,0:02:02.25,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,wow wow oh oh oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.25,0:02:05.75,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,なぁ、わかってるんだろう？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.46,0:02:08.68,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,僕らはいつだって傷だらけで
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.68,0:02:10.87,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悲しみのルーツ断ち切って
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.35,0:02:14.58,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怖くないよ　いつでも傍に感じるから
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.90,0:02:17.27,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,だから　もっと　もっと
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.56,0:02:21.73,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,熱い　力が心満たしてく
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.99,0:02:23.80,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1, 2, 3, 4, 5
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.12,0:02:26.18,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wake！ Up！ Your！ Heart！ Beat！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.34,0:02:29.26,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Blazeに生きていくんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.54,0:02:31.47,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ドキドキ感じて Burning！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.79,0:02:33.32,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Brave and boiling heart
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.32,0:02:35.97,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絆を示せ High！！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.97,0:02:38.04,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Blazeに生きていくんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.20,0:02:40.26,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ドキドキ感じて Burning！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.26,0:02:41.61,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Over Boost！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.61,0:02:42.59,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is a real deal！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.59,0:02:43.61,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No more liars
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.61,0:02:44.84,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ignition's ON, my heart is on
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.84,0:02:46.03,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Fire Fire Fire
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.27,0:02:48.03,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,My blood will burn on
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.03,0:02:51.21,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ah fight on！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.25,0:01:38.05,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当我还是个孩子 在一个疯狂的梦中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.36,0:01:40.13,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我正仰望着那块约定之地
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.13,0:01:44.76,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是我们的梦的形状 喧嚣四起 心脏起跳！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.76,0:01:46.77,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧 让我们共同前往那块土地
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.11,0:01:48.73,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已无法停止
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.98,0:01:53.53,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跳跃吧 穿过白日阴沉 飞入光芒 
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.82,0:01:57.40,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想相信出生于这个世界是一件幸福的事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.40,0:02:00.00,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打开通往新时代的大门
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.00,0:02:02.25,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,wow wow oh oh oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.25,0:02:05.75,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说 你是知道的吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.46,0:02:08.68,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们一直都遍体鳞伤
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.68,0:02:10.87,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,努力斩断悲伤的根源
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.35,0:02:14.58,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要害怕 我们永远能在身边感受到彼此
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.90,0:02:17.27,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 更多 更多
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.56,0:02:21.73,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要将更多炙热的力量填满心灵
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.99,0:02:23.80,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1, 2, 3, 4, 5
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.12,0:02:26.18,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唤醒你的心跳！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.34,0:02:29.26,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让生命绽放光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.54,0:02:31.47,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感受心的脉动  燃烧！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.79,0:02:33.32,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇敢而沸腾的心
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.32,0:02:35.97,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,展现彼此的羁绊 高涨！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.97,0:02:38.04,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让生命绽放光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.20,0:02:40.26,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感受心的脉动  燃烧！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.26,0:02:41.61,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加速到极限！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.61,0:02:42.59,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次是来真的！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.59,0:02:43.61,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要更多谎言
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.61,0:02:44.84,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,装置已点火 心脏已起搏
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.84,0:02:46.03,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火焰 火焰 火焰
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.27,0:02:48.03,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的热血将燃烧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.03,0:02:51.21,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 开战吧！
